text: A cozy and cozy little restaurant. We ordered one of the daily lunch sets and the curry pork chop rice. The curry itself tastes good and the portions are quite generous. Overall, it's a sweet little place that I'd gladly come back to if I'm ever in the neighborhood again.

Cozy little restaurant coupled with excellent and tasty Bento set. Loving it.

The chawamushi is especially good to my liking.

Thanks for the great good

Will be back again

Found this place during a ride. There is nothing to talk about except the Shima hokke .
It's gooddddddd~
It's a bit on the pricey side, Shima hokke, rice, miso, and hot tea at $33. Yet again, it's good.

Had a Christmas dinner with my friend. We got the buddy bento set and it was packed with the best offerings from Tamako Meal. Enjoyed the authentic Japanese flavors and it was heartwarming, the staff was also friendly and well versed on the menu. Hope to visit again soon
Excellent service received from a friendly & courteous staff at the entrance. Very delectable foods & beverages to enjoys with! Thank you for the wonderful foods at prepared!
